### PHẦN 8 - TEST LUỒNG HOẠT ĐỘNG HOÀN CHỈNH
### ChatService Outbox Pattern Flow Test

### ============================================
### STEP 1: Publish Policy Created Event
### ============================================
POST http://localhost:5003/api/event/publish-policy-created
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyId": "POL-001",
  "policyNumber": "POL-20241227-0001",
  "customerId": "CUST-001",
  "productId": "PROD-001",
  "premiumAmount": 1500.00
}

### Expected Response:
### {
###   "message": "Event saved to database successfully",
###   "eventType": "PolicyCreated",
###   "policyNumber": "POL-20241227-0001"
### }

### ============================================
### STEP 2: Check Outbox Status (Immediately after)
### ============================================
GET http://localhost:5003/api/event/outbox/status

### Expected Response (if background job hasn't run yet):
### {
###   "unprocessedCount": 1,
###   "recentUnprocessedMessages": [
###     {
###       "id": 1,
###       "type": "ChatService.Events.PolicyCreated",
###       "createdAt": "2024-12-27T10:30:00Z",
###       "isProcessed": false
###     }
###   ]
### }

### ============================================
### STEP 3: Wait 1-2 seconds, then check again
### ============================================
GET http://localhost:5003/api/event/outbox/status

### Expected Response (after background job processed):
### {
###   "unprocessedCount": 0,
###   "recentUnprocessedMessages": []
### }

### ============================================
### STEP 4: Check Outbox Monitor (if available)
### ============================================
GET http://localhost:5003/api/outbox-monitor/stats

