### ============================================
### NOTES
### ============================================
### 
### FLOW VERIFICATION:
### 1. Send POST request → Event saved to database (STEP 1-2)
### 2. Check outbox status immediately → Should see unprocessed message
### 3. Wait 1-2 seconds → Background job processes message (STEP 3-6)
### 4. Check outbox status again → Should be empty (message deleted)
### 5. Check RabbitMQ management UI → Should see message in exchange
### 
### EXPECTED TIMELINE:
### T+0s:   POST request → Event saved to DB
### T+0s:   GET status → unprocessedCount = 1
### T+1s:   Background job runs → Read → Publish → Delete
### T+2s:   GET status → unprocessedCount = 0
### 
### TROUBLESHOOTING:
### - If unprocessedCount stays > 0: Check RabbitMQ connection
### - If no logs appear: Check OutboxSendingService is registered
### - If events not deleted: Check Outbox.DeleteMessageAsync() implementation
